here is the step:

following [this tutorial](https://www.codementor.io/engineerapart/getting-started-with-postgresql-on-mac-osx-are8jcopb) to create a user and connect it to prosgres 

the tutorial is about getting started with psql database with mac.

create the sql alchemy url for psql here is the syntax

postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/database_ame

then use flask sqlalchemy to creat a database 

flask db init
flask db migrate 
flask db upgrate

requirement : pip install psycopg2  , pip install sqlalchemy and pandas

connect to the database using 

engine = create_engine(url) # with the engine you can query the database without any problem
